Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:33.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我早已是不淨之身
