Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:40.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:42.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}鳥嗎
