Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:44.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我若不把拋手包表演好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽豈不是成了在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一定要作到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:53.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親  母親正在看著呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}竟然被這種粗糙的箭…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:21.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:26.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}保護著我辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然是段短暫的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人  給您水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒事  給神奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是我的命令  喝了它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就剩這些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知道了  三個人分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把剩下的全喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:24.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣三個人靠在一起  簡直
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就像是一個和睦的家庭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「真正的家族就是緊密地靠在一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這話不是你說的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}的確是那樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們兩個有什麼願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼突然問起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊 突然被你這麼一問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:51.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算拼了命  也要衝出包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:54.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}至少也要讓神奈活著逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的話有個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想和神奈大人與柳也大人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}永遠生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也許是個不錯的願望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在某個寧靜的地方  搭建一個小小的庵堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}養家餬口的話  我是可以想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}種地也好  打獵也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果是在海邊的話  還也可以打魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:20.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}非要去的話  西邊的暖海應該不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海  是什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽人說是一個寬廣無盡的大水池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過沒有親眼見過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然是一個水池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過裏面的水都是鹽水喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又在騙我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是真的  神奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且  海和天空一樣寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}鯛魚和鮑魚也可以隨便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:57.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就要看我能撈回多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:05.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海邊的小村中也會舉行夏日祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  在哪都會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}下回我們三個人一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}光看沒有意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:23.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢也不全是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們兩個絕對不可以離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:39.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與柳也在一起  我都忘記了自己的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是我最後的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們要永遠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:00.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要怕！放箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是降魔的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:34.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}法師們正在向神奈大人施法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直念下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了消滅翼人  保衛這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要怕犧牲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈 再飛高點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再高點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再飛高點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:50.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳… 也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:22.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈—！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人 您要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不管是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把神奈弄成這樣的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我死前能殺一個是一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}攔著我的話就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就請殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可不是在嚇唬你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到變成惡鬼的柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  我還能聽到神奈大人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:05.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:06.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過我可以聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以聽到神奈大人的哭聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想你們是神奈備命的護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}奉師傅之命  來迎接你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}召見我們的  是一位叫智德法師的高僧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}智德對神奈的事大概都已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在這做寺院中也曾經住過翼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:40.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從那以後  這個寺院就成為了看護翼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}時而也會援助翼人的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}按照智德的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}翼人們代代相傳著星之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:52.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從很早以前就開始  傳授了人類很多知識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其中的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是現在我們所說的法術的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼叫繼承夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:05.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個  我們無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正因為翼人有這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以經常被掌權者控制起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}漸漸成為了戰爭的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是一個人承受了在戰爭中殺死的人們的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所謂的「不淨」就是這個含義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}攻入靈山的是朝廷的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說是為了毀滅「翼人」這種信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}統一人們的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}智德說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也許神奈就是這個世界上最後一個翼人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}智德大師  我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:43.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請您無論如何將法術傳授給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}於是我們便在這個寺院中住了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}據說裏葉是百年一見的奇才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣過了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那麼  開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}招魂的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}使用這個咒語後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就應該可以看到神奈大人在做什麼樣的夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也你起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼不動  為什麼不抬起頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不允許把我留下一個人離去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:33.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:37.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼大家  只留下我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:45.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈在做的夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:55.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是說她正在天空中的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:58.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直做著這樣的夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}靈山僧侶們施展的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在依然折磨著神奈大人的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}此外還有她從母親那繼承下來的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:13.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這些都會另與翼人親近的人漸漸衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不久便會死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的傷口總無法復原也是這個原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:22.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我自己可以施法避開那些詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但柳也大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的死期是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從現在開始  撐不了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:32.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:37.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}禁錮著神奈大人的咒語終有一天會瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:43.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那時神奈大人的靈魂會回歸大地  輪迴轉生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  把翼人的靈魂注入人類的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就好比讓一個小的容器去承受大海的水量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:55.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}水還沒有注完  容器就破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以神奈大人的靈魂還無法得到復原
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就再次輪迴轉生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經沒有多少時日了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有什麼解救神奈的辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}辦法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請留下一個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人的意志就可以傳乘下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果我們的孩子依然沒能完成  還有孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}孫子也沒能完成的話  還有曾孫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他們都會繼承柳也大人的意志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:33.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後終有一天會找到解救神奈大人的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我來幫助您…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:43.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:48.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我生命中剩餘的時間會全部用在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}時光緩緩流逝著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:57.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}石屋裏有我編寫的「翼人傳」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:02.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不久即將出生的我們的孩子  尋找神奈的靈魂時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這本書一定可以成為他的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後裏葉會教他法術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果是繼承著裏葉的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一定會成為擅長法術的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也許可以最終找到我們沒能想到的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:21.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要時光流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的旅途就能繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了尋找那對無可取代的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了能再次與她相見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經沒有什麼可留戀的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}鳥在飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:42.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算忘記也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忘記神奈也忘記我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:50.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幸福的生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人和柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今後也會在身邊為我指引道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這才是我的妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:12.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}謝謝你… 裏葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}下雨了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明明是晴空萬里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  裏葉我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:36.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈在天空的彼岸等著我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好的  我陪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海角天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:53.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:57.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:20:59.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才為止我一直在什麼人的身旁來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在一個重要的人的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:09.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}腦子空空的想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:26.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  你是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:27.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還不會飛吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:37.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯… 留下它就這樣走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧  走幾步回頭看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有跟過來的話就拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！ 跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要和我一起走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊  那一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:01.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}走嘍～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:42.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明天開始就放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:45.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這東西還和你真親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:47.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我給他起名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.10,0:23:47.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}叫小空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:49.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就沒有別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:51.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不許
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:58.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}總不能一直這樣生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:01.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:03.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就無法努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:05.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:07.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.93,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:10.28,AIR Title2-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1360,1086)}{\fad(1000,0)}光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:52.70,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}消失的航跡雲 我們目送遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:56.41,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因眩目而逃開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:01:06.46,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因懊悔而放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:13.80,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}尚未抵達之地仍在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:20.76,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}只有將願望深藏心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:29.11,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}孩子們走在夏日的鐵軌上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:35.78,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,640)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}手中是將振翅高飛的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:43.79,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}消失的航跡雲 我們追了又追
